I work at the Wildlife Health Center, part of VetMed at UC Davis, doing their publications (print and electronic). I keep a blog, [http://magpienest.org/feathersofhope/ Feathers of Hope], with my partner (we are Pica and Numenius there) which explores nature and place (and some baseball: go Red Sox). We were founding members of the [http://www.magpienest.org/scgi-bin/wiki.pl Ecotone Wiki].
